   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The Calculation Summary page displays aggregated Price, Freight Amount (if specified in the order line item), Quantity for a combination of Customer, and Product based on the setting made at the benefit level. You can see the total freight charges applicable at the schedule level in the Schedule Period Information section. Billing consumes the details provided in the calculation summary.</p>
